text: #CityandPolicy About 420,000 #COVID19 #vaccine doses had been administered in Shenyang, Shenyang CDC said Thur, adding the city has established a temporary vaccination site of 4,000 m2. With 60 inoculation tables, the site can ensure inoculation of at least 6,000 doses per day. https://t.co/BKz046sM4D
